etaining their shape.","When emptying mixing bowl, the syrup can be reserved and reduced to pour over ice cream or any poached fruit.","Honey ice cream may be used instead.","Frozen raspberries can be used. If using frozen berries, omit 1 tbsp water.","Add 1 tbsp kirsch to the coulis for an adults-only kick of flavour."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","35m","6 portions"]}